==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Classically
<hw>Clas"sic*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a classical
manner; according to the manner of classical authors.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In the manner of classes; according to a regular
order of classes or sets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Classicism</ent>⟦br⟧
